            "content": [
              {
                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "Contoso Electronics offers a lineup of consumer electronics and technology solutions that includes smartphones, laptops, tablets, and smart home devices .\n\nFeatured Contoso products include :\n\n- **Contoso Smartphone X1** — **$799**  \n  6.5\" OLED display, 128GB/256GB storage options, 48MP AI-enhanced main camera, 4500mAh battery with fast charging.\n\n- **Contoso Laptop Pro 15** — **$1,299**  \n  15.6\" 4K IPS display, Intel Core i7 (latest generation), 16GB RAM, 512GB NVMe SSD, up to 12 hours battery life.\n\n- **Contoso Smart Home Hub** — **$149**  \n  WiFi 6, Bluetooth 5.0, Zigbee; built-in Contoso AI Assistant; compatible with 500+ smart home devices.\n\nSupport and warranty details: Contoso provides customer support via **support@contoso.com** and **1-800-CONTOSO** (Mon–Fri, 9AM–6PM EST), and products include a **standard 1-year manufacturer warranty** with optional extended coverage purchasable within 30 days .",
